# Assignment_1

Copying a content from A.csv file to another B.csv file. 
--> Attributes/fields 
Name, Age, class, Div, Teacher 
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------


    1}Check if Original_Record.csv exists.
      If not, create it and let the user enter data.

    2}Verify Read Access given to the original file.

    3}Check/Create Temporary_Record.csv.

    4}Verify Write Access to the temporary file.

    5}Ensure the Original File has Data.

    6}Clear the Temporary File if it contains old data.

    7}Copy Data from the original file to the temporary file.

   8}Compare File Sizes to ensure complete copy.

   9}Preview First 5 Lines of the copied file.
